author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: "pm install output ends with a verification summary (activation status, registered commands/types, health ok/degraded) equivalent to a light package-doctor pass; failures keep the existing per-target failure rows; covered by specs"
