body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/473\n\nFold a light verification pass into `pm install` output (activation status, registered commands/item types, health verdict) so agents skip the follow-up `pm package doctor` in the happy path. Builds on the multi-target install aggregation shipped for pm-hj9h (per-target success/failure rows)."
